com.cyc.query.metrics

Interface InferenceMetrics

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Collection<InferenceMetric>, InferenceParameterValue, Iterable<InferenceMetric>, Set<InferenceMetric>

    public interface InferenceMetrics
extends Set<InferenceMetric>, InferenceParameterValue
    A Set of InferenceMetric values. Inference metrics are a way of telling Cyc's inference engine to collect a certain type of data for later inspection. The most common metrics are in StandardInferenceMetric.
